::DrillBit::

He was drilling at the armor plate when a glance of the eye, saw the
missile coming for him. He moved back and the missiles hit the weakend
armor he had been working on.(And sice Cyber Wolf posted that all things
like that were now destroyed lets say that took it out.)
The shockwave sent DrillBit back in to a computer, but he was quickly
up.
"DrillBit, TERRORIZE!" He transformed to bot mode, and dashed out the
break in the armor to freedom.
"Come on, Killfest, it's going to blow!" DrillBit made it to where
DarkFate was.
"Nice plan, with the comp virus."
